emission and (ii) spontaneous emergence of tilted\naccretion disk-jet flows, even in the absence of any tilt in the progenitor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Nov 2021 02:15:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 21:07:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
