 SNe could be\naccurate distance indicators which should not be excluded from future\ncosmological analyses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 18:05:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Feb 2022 19:05:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
