 a densification of porous framework at the contact zone.\nFinally, we measured the fracture toughness using a cube corner indenter to\nstudy the resistance of monoliths against cracking failure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 19:07:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-01"}
