tion. Additionally, we found that spectrally hard ULXs show\nfewer line detections than soft ULXs, indicating some difference in their\naccretion geometry and orientation, possibly causing over-ionisation of plasma\nby the harder spectral energy distributions of harder ULXs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 19:39:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
