n to the Br\\'ezis-Nirenberg problem \\[ -\\Delta u+\\lambda\nu=\\mu |u|^{2^*-2}u,\\quad u\\in H^1_0(\\Omega), \\] for $\\mu>0$,\n$-\\lambda_1(\\Omega)<\\lambda<0$ for all $N\\geq 4$, a result which is new in\ndimensions $N=4,5$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 22:59:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-01"}
