 accounts in trend manipulation as compared to bots.\nFurthermore, we present two case studies of hashtag-wars and anti-state\npropaganda to implicate the real-world application of our research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2021 06:30:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-01"}
