irectional\nand unidirectional jet activity observed to have been initiated from the\ninitially localized bursts in the corona. The transient nature of coronal\nbursts and the associated plasma flows or jets along with their dynamics could\nprovide a benchmark for magnetic reconnection models of coronal bursts and\njets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2021 13:15:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Oct 2021 14:21:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
